{"tid":233551,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"巴絲打留底個溝唔到/行唔到尾,反正就會記掛一世既人","createTime":"2017-05-07T15:29:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-09T12:26:16.000Z","uid":114722,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d8b31229e39f58e90d636e498b2889a2e5d0b18d","tid":233551,"uid":114722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:29:07.000Z","msg":"如題。<br />\n    做左cdrm咁9耐 終於的起心肝開番個ac<br />\n    大概我會記掛一世既人 係初戀<br />\n    差唔多7年感情 小過三 分過手 上過床 打過交 同過居<br />\n    佢係我既完美男神 籃球神 中學神射手 所有朋友都覺得對佢好好<br />\n    成熟穩重又搞笑 處事手法圓滑 係佢後面我永遠受保護<br />\n    為人樂觀識得體諒人 係佢教識我所有野要學識包容人 每樣野都有樂觀既一面<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">    (造就左好多宜家既人會讚我既優點 包括現任男朋友)</span></span><br />\n    佢擁有好多 但佢眼中只會有我 佢個世界得我 我個世界都得佢<br />\n    我永遠係佢第一 佢屋企人當我係新抱<br />\n    我信呢世人入面唔會再識到遇到一個咁愛我 我咁愛既人<br />\n    我好多謝個天比係我人生入面識到你<br />\n    最後行唔到落去 起碼比我知道點樣去愛一個人 一個人可以點去愛 我係幾咁被愛過<br />\n    上到大學 先見識到身邊既人 邊愛得咁多 汁番劑 各取所需 大家陪下大家<br />\n    Just For Fun, Fun完, Fuck完, 出番呵 又係一個又一個畢身既男女神.....<br />\n    呢個世界黎多幾多次都好 我都冇後悔過比第一次呢個人<br />\n    <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8d450b186d9654c37b240c06b6c138413a8cebb","tid":233551,"uid":17881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:30:59.000Z","msg":"講到天上有地下無 點解又會散呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce6e1cb503d928ad821540d180d619965651253","tid":233551,"uid":35106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:31:49.000Z","msg":"有一個單戀過既人 但同佢反左面了被block<br />\n點都好 佢令我有改變既原動力<br />\n令我真正正視自己既缺點<br />\n多謝佢出現<br />\n好想親口道歉"},{"pid":"67f4b2bf7637c796921b4cc23fc186c43d09352b","tid":233551,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:32:07.000Z","msg":"中學第一次追 用左幾年 最後無結果 不過同你一樣 真係學左好q多野 例如點同女相處<br />\n尊重每一個人空間"},{"pid":"55e7a736bc89669332d57907e6b0c484f9f4f42c","tid":233551,"uid":114722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:37:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講到天上有地下無 點解又會散呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n價值觀 人大左就唔同 越大越遠 得個愛字好難從細行到大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"473629588c54abaad55c5a23c30ccce4ce521d95","tid":233551,"uid":114722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:38:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中學第一次追 用左幾年 最後無結果 不過同你一樣 真係學左好q多野 例如點同女相處<br />\n尊重每一個人空間</blockquote><br />\n學到野 長大先係真理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bcbd0d46d917b2d3bd14b98abcc35312493a5ac","tid":233551,"uid":99048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T15:44:55.000Z","msg":"樓主個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ngay? <img src=\"/assets/faces/no